    <detaileddescription>
<para>Helper class that manages an interrupt flag, and allows a thread or signal to interrupt another thread.</para>
<para>This class is safe to be used in a signal handler. If sending an interrupt from a signal handler is not necessary, the more lightweight <ref refid="class_c_thread_interrupt" kindref="compound">CThreadInterrupt</ref> class can be used instead. </para>
